title: Hit List
subTitle: Vijay's life turns into a living hell when a mysterious masked figure abducts his family. Forced into a dark world of violence, he becomes an unwilling assassin, targeting the kidnapper's enemies.

title: Yudhra
subTitle: A vengeful youth infiltrates a dangerous cartel to avenge the death of his parents. As he delves deeper, he uncovers shocking truths about his past that challenge his resolve and moral boundaries.

title: Dhartiputra
subTitle: Yashpal tries to rape Jeeva and her husband, Shiva, stops him while she manages to escape. However, Yashpal kills him and she vows to avenge his death.

title: Yuvarathnaa
subTitle: When the college is now on the verge of closing, a dedicated principal must fight against the privatisation of education system to save the college.

title: The Faith Show
subTitle: Romildo Ribeiro Soares, a Brazilian televangelist, stresses the importance of faith in the Almighty and explains inner life and how to condition it for the world.

title: Ek Joshila
subTitle: Vamsi is hell-bent on seeking revenge and rescue his lover Krishnaveni, from the clutches of an evil landlord, Basavanna, who murdered his best friend.

title: Vijay The Master
subTitle: Troubled alcoholic teacher JD goes to work at a juvenile reform school. When he realises a dangerous criminal is using students to cover up his crimes, JD sets out to stop him.

title: Aranmanai 4
subTitle: Suspicious about his sister's death, Saravanan, a lawyer, tries to solve the mystery behind it, only to discover a mysteriously dark force at play.

title: Sikandar
subTitle: A passionate young man faces off against a corrupted system, challenging the existing authorities and injustice that take away the rights of common people.

title: Jawan
subTitle: Driven by a personal vendetta, a man sets out to rectify the wrongs in the society to keep a promise made years ago.

title: Shivam Bhaje
subTitle: A young loan recovery agent gets entangled in an unexpected accident that turns his life upside down. To avert the crisis, he must find a way to handle the highly destructive threat.

title: Skanda
subTitle: After Rayudu and Ranjith Reddy's children elope, the CMs turn against each other. However, when a college student kidnaps Reddy's daughter, a revenge saga unravels.

subTitle: An orphan boy, strives to cope with life after losing his parents. However, when he grows up, he crosses paths with two college students who are his reincarnated parents.

subTitle: Romildo Ribeiro Soares, a Brazilian televangelist, stresses the importance of faith in the Almighty and explains inner life and how to condition it for the world.

subTitle: A police officer saves a girl from being kidnapped and later looks into her failed abduction. Although the motive for the crime initially seems unclear, the clues soon lead her to a drug mafia.

title: Radhe

subTitle: Upon learning about his father's disappearance at the border, Jeete believes that his father is captured and sets out to rescue him in Pakistan.

title: Antim: The Final Truth
subTitle: Rahul runs away from his poverty-stricken village life to become a gangster in the city. There, he locks horns with an upstanding policeman who tries to set him on the right path.

title: Khuda Haafiz
subTitle: When a financial crisis leaves Sameer and Nargis jobless, they resort to taking up a job in the Middle East. But when Nargis goes missing on arrival, Sameer sets out on a bloody quest to find her.

title: Badla Naag Ka
subTitle: A fearless man hurts a snake when it tries to attack his lover. Later, he tries to protect himself from the snake which is trying to exact its revenge.

title: Zero
subTitle: A vertically-challenged bachelor with a larger-than-life personality discovers his life's purpose through his relationships with two wildly different women.

title: The Faith Show

subTitle: Charlie, a good-for-nothing young man, becomes entangled in fast-paced, side-splitting monkey business between a runaway gorilla and a high-profile wanted fraudster disguised as one.

subTitle: Raj and Priya, a married couple, hire Madhubala, a prostitute, as the surrogate mother of their child. Trouble brews when Madhubala falls in love with Raj and insists on keeping the child.

subTitle: Vijay Govind, a young lecturer in a college, wishes to get married at the earliest. He tries to woo Geetha, an independent and a level-headed woman, who is not easy to convince.

title: Hum Aapke Hain Kaun

title: Crew

title: Vettaiyan

title: Bholaa
subTitle: After getting out of prison with the desire to meet his daughter, Bholaa's plans are interrupted by a well-orchestrated drug bust.
